      • replace

        default <B> Functor<F,B> replace(B b)
        Replace is equivalent to map(const(b)) // f.replace(b) == f.map(const(b))) where const(b) creates a function that always returns b.
        Type Parameters:
        B - the type of the contents of the new Functor.
        Parameters:
        b - the value to be insterted into a Functor.
        Returns:
        the Functor containing b.
